msgctxt "72_Distracted Woman"
msgid ""
"Where was that motsunabe place? I'm starvin' for some good ol' fashioned "
"organ meat!"
msgstr ""
"Dov'era quel locale di motsunabe? Ho una fame boia di quelle buone, vecchie "
"frattaglie!"
